<section class="ecosystem" id="ecosystem" aria-labelledby="ecosystem-title">
  <h2 id="ecosystem-title">Part of something bigger</h2>
  <p class="ecosystem-text">
    proto IM is one piece of the ATProto messaging stack. We don't do everything, on purpose.
    <strong><a href="https://www.germnetwork.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Germ</a></strong> handles
    persistent, end-to-end encrypted DMs with MLS. <strong><a href="https://roomy.space/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Roomy</a></strong> handles
    open-source group chat and community spaces, like Discord but decentralized.
    <strong>We handle video calls and the buddy list.</strong> Three independent projects, one open network.
  </p>
</section>
